"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/458607","Department for Transport","false","2016-03-16","<p>Funding for major local transport schemes is devolved as part of the Local Growth Fund to which the Department is contributing over £7billion. It is for LEPs to determine the priority projects in their areas. I understand that schemes that Solent LEP is undertaking in Southampton include the Cross Solent Connectivity Project, junction improvements near the Western Docks, and the recently completed Station Quarter scheme.</p><p> </p>","Harrogate and Knaresborough","Andrew Jones",,"2016-03-16T10:22:45.693Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/458607/answer","Biography information for Andrew Jones","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/458607/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/458607/answer",,,,,"27","Transport","Transport","2016-03-08","Transport: Southampton","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Transport, what recent progress has been made on devolving local transport schemes to local enterprise partnerships (LEP); and if he will assess the effect of such policies on the work of the Solent LEP in developing Southampton's infrastructure.","false","Biography information for Royston Smith","Southampton, Itchen","Royston Smith","30327"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/458608","Department for Transport","false","2016-03-16","<p>The Government is continuing to actively consider how best to address problems wheelchair users face when using taxis and private hire vehicles, including the possible commencement of Section 165 of the Equality Act 2010.</p>","Harrogate and Knaresborough","Andrew Jones",,"2016-03-16T16:27:16.293Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/458608/answer","Biography information for Andrew Jones","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/458608/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/458608/answer",,,,,"27","Transport","Transport","2016-03-08","Taxis: Wheelchairs","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Transport, pursuant to the Answer of 27 January 2016 to Question 23178, if he will announce a date for the introduction of section 165 of the Equality Act 2010.","false","Biography information for Richard Fuller","Bedford","Richard Fuller","30346"
